{"tid":188787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台青年讚上海消費方便屌打台灣 掀網路論戰","createTime":"2017-04-06T02:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T11:18:25.000Z","uid":13468,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5030d68a96dfbe24cda2302424a87f3313b95035","tid":188787,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"台青年讚上海消費方便屌打台灣 掀網路論戰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2027143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2027143&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=80a8a667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2027143&h=a6996daf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2027143</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-04-05  23:44<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕25歲台灣青年日前拍攝影片，讚揚中國方便到害死人，甚至呼籲台灣人「不要再認為臺灣很屌很方便了，其實真的沒什麼。」這番言論在網路上引起討論，其中筆名「人渣文本」的輔大教師周偉航則諷刺，羊毛出在羊身上，中國消費再方便也是要付錢。<br />\n<br />\n「弱肌店長Jeremy」在影片中指出，上海是一個很適合打拼、進步很快的地方，且上海很方便，網路速度屌打台灣，生活靠著一隻手機就可以完成，因為手機可以付款、可以叫車、叫外賣，不需要靠現金這種東西，他甚至呼籲台灣人，不要再做井底之蛙，臺灣其實真的沒什麼。<br />\n<br />\n這番言論也引起網友熱烈討論，其中，周偉航表示，羊毛出在羊身上，中國的消費再方便還是要付錢，等中國食衣住行都不用錢再來說吧，不過「中國六十年前就搞過食衣住行都不用錢，然後很多人就死掉了。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，自由台灣黨政策部主任溫朗東也在臉書PO文，中國好的就學，不好的就不要，不知道好不好，就要仔細評估，不要照單全收。愛家園就像愛媽媽一樣，別人的媽媽看起來如何，都是別人的，愛自己的媽媽，不需要因為她是最好的。<br />\n<br />\n相關影片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=uOECtLmTrJ0&amp;ebc=ANyPxKpuVYKXO0w0W2PBMu_OptpuyIxsJz7LxNRLHsyJigpXAUSrS7UhuthjFqHLvOOHcFqhSvnXLRLs81zJEIFXvbsMR4-rgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuOECtLmTrJ0%26ebc%3DANyPxKpuVYKXO0w0W2PBMu_OptpuyIxsJz7LxNRLHsyJigpXAUSrS7UhuthjFqHLvOOHcFqhSvnXLRLs81zJEIFXvbsMR4-rgQ&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=cc0d5b10\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=uOECtLmTrJ0&amp;ebc=ANyPxKpuVYKXO0w0W2PBMu_OptpuyIxsJz7LxNRLHsyJigpXAUSrS7UhuthjFqHLvOOHcFqhSvnXLRLs81zJEIFXvbsMR4-rgQ</a>"},{"pid":"9f9545ae7b0068a975d4fb66d4bbd74bd9780588","tid":188787,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10a9980ddb1ba7fe8c9fa97ae37513d451375428","tid":188787,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"對香港都係同一招<br />\n話中國點好點好，香港人唔好以為自己好勁乜乜77"},{"pid":"db29d8d67c58c429a6faef19b89e3c24f376428d","tid":188787,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:03:27.000Z","msg":"可能因為文化原因，台灣確實係慢一拍<br />\n<br />\n上次去高雄有d cafe連wifi都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f9c33a0a3842346a21f95964368953ae524232","tid":188787,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"網路速度屌打台灣，生活靠著一隻手機就可以完成，因為手機可以付款、可以叫車、叫外賣，不需要靠現金這種東西<br />\n<br />\n鄰國個4G其實唔穩定，好多地方收唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛的係好方便，不過只限晴天時間，落狗屎果陣係街同用電話call都超難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d2cb98600763d34b221ee31643e8d973c6ca36","tid":188787,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能因為文化原因，台灣確實係慢一拍<br />\n<br />\n上次去高雄有d cafe連wifi都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港都唔係間間有喎，類比錯誤"},{"pid":"a843e78e19d59f193a55da3148bd7f896b079979","tid":188787,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能因為文化原因，台灣確實係慢一拍<br />\n<br />\n上次去高雄有d cafe連wifi都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"